1. *Ponudio* sam joj da mi pomogne oko projekta. (I offered her to help me with the project.)
2. Oni su *ponudili* dobru cenu za ovaj automobil. (They offered a good price for this car.)
3. Kada *ponuditi* svoj proizvod, treba imati dobar marketing plan. (When offering your product, you should have a good marketing plan.)
4. Ona neće *ponuditi* nikakvu pomoć ako ne zatražite. (She won't offer any help if you don't ask.)
5. Moramo *ponuditi* više opcija za kupce. (We need to offer more options for customers.)
6. *Ponudi* mi neki savet kako da rešim ovaj problem. (Offer me some advice on how to solve this problem.)
7. Oni su *ponudili* novu poziciju menadžera. (They offered a new manager position.)
8. Želeli su da *ponude* svoje usluge po nižoj ceni. (They wanted to offer their services at a lower price.)
9. *Ponudila* se da nam pomogne oko organizacije događaja. (She offered to help us with event organization.)
10. Nisam siguran da li će *ponuditi* kvalitetan proizvod. (I'm not sure if they will offer a quality product.)